<table border="0" width=75%>
<tr> <td> <h1> NCA </h1> </tr></td>

<tr><td>
This is a simple matlab implementation of <a href="http://www.cs.toronto.edu/~hinton/absps/nca.pdf">this</a> NIPS04 paper titled "Neighbourhood Components Analysis" by Jacob Goldberger, Sam Roweis, Geoff Hinton and
Ruslan Salakhutdinov.  Hopefully it will be useful for something.<p>
